Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.93,0:00:15.02,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Aw... Can't get down?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.35,0:00:19.01,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Poor kitty...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.07,0:00:22.67,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, could you close your eyes for a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.29,0:00:26.59,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Till I say you can open them again. No peeking!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.39,0:00:30.01,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.01,0:00:32.84,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You can open your eyes now. Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.44,0:00:35.49,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome! How did you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.49,0:00:36.60,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.60,0:00:38.26,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.26,0:00:39.89,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.63,0:00:48.46,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Kawakami!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.08,0:00:51.29,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.29,0:00:52.48,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.76,0:00:56.10,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,School! We're going to be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.58,0:01:09.55,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fs32}Kuttskukiboshi{\i0}\N{\i0\fs27}- Stars Intertwined -{\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.99,0:01:15.52,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}As thou becometh father to thy son,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.52,0:01:18.68,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}swearest thou an oath unto the world beyond...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.52,0:01:20.56,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Aaya Saitou{shingx originally uses Aya Saitoh, UTW: Aya Saitou} transferred to our class this spring.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.56,0:01:23.23,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,And for the next passage... Saitou.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.23,0:01:29.46,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To me, her voice is more beautiful than any other sound in the world.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.39,0:01:44.32,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And the wind exists...{\i0}{}{}{}{join?}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.32,0:01:47.89,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}to put a sigh through her hair...{\i0}{}{}{}{}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.79,0:01:52.49,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...but this protein known as haemoglobin, found in red blood cells...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.49,0:02:01.06,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fad(0,800)}Just her presence was more important than anything else in the world.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.75,0:02:12.15,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kawakami...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.15,0:02:13.99,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kawakami!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.55,0:02:17.79,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.79,0:02:20.01,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,And your face is pretty red.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.01,0:02:21.31,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.31,0:02:23.35,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, no. Nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.35,0:02:26.49,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That blush in her cheeks, that right there is the haemoglobin.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.37,0:02:29.02,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you'll all remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.02,0:02:33.16,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then, everyone stay focused and disciplined over the summer break!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.16,0:02:34.24,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Class dismissed!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.24,0:02:36.62,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.62,0:02:38.21,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Bow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.48,0:02:45.41,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Call me if there's something you don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.41,0:02:46.29,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.29,0:02:47.94,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Only for the parts I know, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.94,0:02:49.56,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it. Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.64,0:03:08.63,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do our usual thing today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.84,0:03:16.33,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.69,0:03:24.55,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Had enough already?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.55,0:03:27.59,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... I can't take any more...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.45,0:03:32.43,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It moved! A new record!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.43,0:03:35.46,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I really think your powers are getting stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.88,0:03:40.73,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Saitou... You treat me like a guinea pig or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.73,0:03:41.67,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Exper—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.67,0:03:45.73,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,When you had that traffic accident a year ago, did anything else change?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.73,0:03:48.23,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.23,0:03:50.30,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,By the time I woke up at the hospital,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.30,0:03:53.04,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I was already like this, somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.04,0:03:54.12,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.12,0:03:57.61,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It must have been the shock that brought out your powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.61,0:03:59.70,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have other powers, like predicting the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.70,0:04:04.95,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... I'm just able to move objects without touching them, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.10,0:04:08.74,Main",,0259,0000,0000,,— Can we stop now?\N— No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.74,0:04:12.53,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to make those powers a secret between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.56,0:04:16.87,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.02,0:04:33.97,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{before in utw: Catch it, catch it!}{}No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.97,0:04:35.15,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That was close...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.60,0:04:39.80,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know why, but this tree didn't burn down even in the air raids.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.80,0:04:43.08,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I think there's a great well of energy sleeping in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.25,0:04:47.58,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{utw: I want you to take that energy.}Let's receive some of its energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.13,0:04:53.57,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.86,0:05:00.16,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As long as I keep this secret, I have no choice but to do what she says.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.36,0:05:02.80,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.80,0:05:07.37,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Actually, there's another secret that she doesn't know about.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.35,0:05:10.79,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The fact that ever since we met...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.79,0:05:15.80,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've been in love with everything about Aaya Saitou.{\i0}{utw: I fell in love with Saitou Aya,\Neverything about her, at first sight.}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.91,0:05:47.60,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Saitou?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.71,0:06:29.15,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my god!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.15,0:06:31.21,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.76,0:07:03.90,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,The school during summer vacation is somehow... otherworldly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.50,0:07:11.36,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,The empty morning campus seems almost like our own private castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.40,0:07:15.63,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't find one to my liking, so I made it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.63,0:07:17.79,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What, a puzzle ring?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.79,0:07:20.78,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, this isn't a puzzle you can solve.{utw: Intelligence won't separate these.}{it's not a puzzle. These can't be separated normally.}{}{}{}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.78,0:07:22.85,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow... You're so clever.{utw: Amazing.  You're skillful.}{}{}{}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.85,0:07:27.03,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that maybe you'd be able to separate these with your powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.03,0:07:29.40,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? I'm not too sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.40,0:07:31.63,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, you're still experimenting with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.63,0:07:34.20,Main",,0231,0000,0000,,— It's two different matters!\N— Okay, I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.01,0:07:42.56,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do it, after all. Things like these are impossible.{utw: I can't do it, as I thought.  I don't think it's possible.}{}{}{}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.60,0:07:45.39,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Or is it... possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.31,0:07:49.57,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes, it happens before you've realized.{utw: I don't mind if you only remember once in a while.}{}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.53,0:07:55.59,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to try at this every day.{utw: I'd like you to try whenever you have time.}{}{}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.59,0:07:58.87,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,And if you can see the future, tell me immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.87,0:08:02.03,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. But seeing into the future is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.47,0:08:05.44,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Your nails are so pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.18,0:08:08.31,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Aaya, you're wearing mascara?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.31,0:08:10.70,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... Does it look weird...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.00,0:08:12.33,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gorgeous!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.33,0:08:14.67,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You look really cute in anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.67,0:08:17.75,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks! But even if you flatter me—{utw: Praising me won't get you anything, though.}{}{}{}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.63,0:08:20.36,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I have it.{v1: Oh, it came off...}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.35,0:08:24.59,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,And I also brought eyelash curlers.
