Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.65,0:13:06.08,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.43,0:13:08.38,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.38,0:13:09.00,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.36,0:13:17.07,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is coffee all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.07,0:13:20.17,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, no. Sick people need to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.17,0:13:23.68,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... I'm not actually... sick...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.10,0:13:27.45,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,My flow is kind of... heavy today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.17,0:13:29.73,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.73,0:13:31.62,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.98,0:13:35.89,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, you should lie down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.89,0:13:37.41,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, nurse!
