Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.10,0:13:43.57,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,They're my brother's.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.57,0:13:47.14,Main",,0194,0000,0000,,— Wow... So you have a brother.\N— He seldom comes home, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.90,0:13:49.59,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you manage to separate that?
