Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.28,0:13:52.46,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.46,0:13:54.80,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But anyway, here. This is for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.66,0:13:58.22,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I recommend this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.22,0:14:00.72,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been listening to this since junior high...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.72,0:14:03.09,Main",,0246,0000,0000,,— Perhaps you know it?\N— Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.09,0:14:04.71,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? I guess you would.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.71,0:14:07.46,Main",,0272,0000,0000,,— I'm back.\N— Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.70,0:14:10.36,Main",,0224,0000,0000,,— Your friend?\N— Kawakami{tsk, was: Kawagami}, my classmate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.75,0:14:15.44,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to disturb you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.89,0:14:18.28,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.45,0:14:24.36,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.37,0:14:26.90,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
