Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.49,0:15:27.27,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.70,0:15:34.78,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm so happy it was Aaya who found out about my secret powers.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.61,0:15:38.15,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hello? It's me.
