Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.72,0:15:51.26,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's still impossible to separate that, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.63,0:15:54.13,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure it's just because you're not trying hard enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.14,0:15:58.73,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then I'll try harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.64,0:16:20.35,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I'll see you tomorrow at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.35,0:16:22.45,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll text you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.30,0:16:58.23,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.19,0:17:55.83,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she's not home yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.67,0:17:57.66,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.38,0:18:08.68,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
